    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1901-09-13T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1901-09-13T00:00:00-05:00" n="340"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d340">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Emperor of Korea</gloss> to the <gloss
                            type="to">President</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Seoul</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1901-09-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 13, 1901</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The news of your excellency’s wound had greatly grieved and shocked us. We wait
                    with concern the news of your complete recovery. We assure your excellency of
                    our very warm friendship and deep anxiety.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Yi Hiung</hi>,<lb/>
                        <hi rend="italic">Emperor of Korea.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
